<h2>Myanmar: 20 children under the rubble of a monastery in Taungoo</h2>
Some twenty children were trapped under the rubble of a monastery in Taungoo, one of the most important places where were the damage of the earthquake that struck Myanmar. Many buildings collapsed in Mandalay, according to local civil protection sources.
